## 11. Known Issues and Future Work

Known Issues:
- Backend test suite requires a live MongoDB connection and will fail with a dummy URI
- nginx.conf is baked into the Docker image; SSL config changes require a rebuild
- backend.env is regenerated on every Jenkins deploy from Jenkins credentials

